-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- EN — planet_sign (Sun in each sign)
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001','planet_sign','sun','aries',NULL,'en','Sun in Aries','Courage, the energy of new beginnings, and the urge to forge your own path come naturally to you. Overthinking before you leap frustrates you; action is your greatest teacher. Your leadership streak is plainly visible — even when no one tells you to, you instinctively step forward and take the lead.','Bold, full of beginner''s energy, a natural-born leader.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002','planet_sign','sun','taurus',NULL,'en','Sun in Taurus','Stability, tangible beauty, and your own pace are sacred to you. You regard those who rush with suspicion and refuse to abandon your own rhythm. Love, money, nature — whatever is real to you through your five senses becomes the ground your life is built on.','Steady, sensual, moving at your own rhythm.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000003','planet_sign','sun','gemini',NULL,'en','Sun in Gemini','Curiosity, words, and connection are your three pillars. You can learn any subject, but being locked into a single one stifles you. Your life needs variety, flexibility, and a constant stream of new questions; monotony extinguishes your spirit.','Curious, versatile, and communication-loving.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000004','planet_sign','sun','cancer',NULL,'en','Sun in Cancer','Emotional memory, family, and belonging keep you grounded. You may hide what you feel, but you never forget it. You are at your strongest when you are building a home — physical or emotional — with the people you love.','Strong emotional memory, protective, belonging-oriented.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000005','planet_sign','sun','leo',NULL,'en','Sun in Leo','There is a part of you meant to shine — the feeling that the stage is yours is not without reason. You want to be noticed not out of vanity, but because you have earned it. Your generous heart, once you learn to trust it, is your greatest strength.','Generous, wanting to be seen, radiating warm light.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000006','planet_sign','sun','virgo',NULL,'en','Sun in Virgo','A love of detail, service, and the drive toward perfection. You cannot rest until a task is done properly; this is not tedium but an inner calling. Your criticism turns on yourself first — which is why you may seem harsh to others.','A love of detail, work ethic, constant improvement.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000007','planet_sign','sun','libra',NULL,'en','Sun in Libra','Balance, aesthetics, and relationship — the three beats of your heart. Even when you are alone, you see through someone else''s eyes. Seeing both sides when you decide makes you fair; but it can also make you seem indecisive.','Relational, aesthetically sensitive, seeking balance.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008','planet_sign','sun','scorpio',NULL,'en','Sun in Scorpio','You are not satisfied with the surface — truth lies beneath everything, and that is where you go. You bond intensely and live intensely. Destruction and rebirth are the rhythm of your life; when you accept it rather than resist it, you transform.','Deep, transformative, intensely bonding.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000009','planet_sign','sun','sagittarius',NULL,'en','Sun in Sagittarius','Horizons, meaning, and freedom call to you. You do not stay long with anyone who confines you; whether in body or mind, you always travel far and push against limits. Philosophy, travel, learning — that is where you grow.','Broad-minded, freedom-loving, seeking meaning.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000010','planet_sign','sun','capricorn',NULL,'en','Sun in Capricorn','Discipline, responsibility, and the long view — your seriousness is not a luxury but part of who you are. You seem mature from a young age; as you grow older you lighten up and discover how to have fun. You walk toward your goal stubbornly, unafraid of arriving late.','Disciplined, goal-oriented, playing the long game.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000011','planet_sign','sun','aquarius',NULL,'en','Sun in Aquarius','Questioning what is taken for granted comes naturally to you wherever you stand out as different. You care about community, yet you do not speak the language of the crowd. You read the future from the present — which is why you are sometimes misunderstood.','Original, questioning, future-facing.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000012','planet_sign','sun','pisces',NULL,'en','Sun in Pisces','Your boundaries are permeable — you take in both beauty and heaviness. You are creative, intuitive, and compassionate. To avoid losing yourself, you need to learn to set physical boundaries from time to time.','Intuitive, compassionate, creative, permeable.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),

-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- EN — aspect
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000020','aspect','sun','moon','trine','en','Sun ↔ Moon (harmonious aspect / trine)','Your inner "what I ought to do" and "what I want to feel" usually face the same direction. Being yourself does not cost you much effort; your rational decisions generally align with your emotional needs.','Your thoughts and feelings are in harmony.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000021','aspect','sun','moon','square','en','Sun ↔ Moon (tension aspect / square)','Two voices inside you are constantly negotiating: "I should do this" versus "but I don''t feel it." This tension may seem exhausting, yet it is the engine of a deep self-awareness — you are learning to take both your mind and your heart into account.','Able to transform the tension between mind and heart.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000022','aspect','mars','saturn','square','en','Mars ↔ Saturn (tension aspect / square)','Your "act now" impulse and your "think, make a plan" voice are in constant conflict. This clash protects you from hasty decisions but can sometimes paralyze you. In time, you learn to find your own balance between action and patience.','The tension between action and patience.','professional',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000023','aspect','venus','jupiter','sextile','en','Venus ↔ Jupiter (harmonious aspect / sextile)','Expressing love comes naturally to you. You are generous and give freely to those you love; giving without expecting return nourishes your soul. You are inclined to notice the beautiful moments of life — this is not coincidence but a talent.','Generous, seeing the beauty in life.','warm',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000024','aspect','sun','pluto','conjunction','en','Sun ⊕ Pluto (conjunction)','Your identity is intertwined with an intense transformative force. Collapses and rebirths are ordinary in your life; you emerge from each crisis as a different self. Power dynamics both attract you and, whether you like it or not, put you to the test.','An identity defined through transformation.','direct',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),

-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- EN — sign_house
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
('81000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000040','sign_house','scorpio','8',NULL,'en','Scorpio in the 8th House','The 8th house is the house of transformation, shared resources, and the hidden. With Scorpio here, these themes grow even more intense: deep relationships, inheritance, and rising out of crisis are your natural soil. Staying on the surface unsettles you; you have an inner drive to see what is real.','A field of deep transformation.','professional',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL),

-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- EN — misc (Wikipedia editorial context notes)
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001','misc','wiki_astrology','overview',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Overview of astrology','Astrology is treated as a historical interpretive tradition that draws meaningful connections between celestial bodies and human character, behavioral patterns, and life events. In modern product language this topic should not be presented as definitive judgment or scientific prediction; it should be used within a symbolic, cultural, and self-awareness-focused frame.','A general note positioning astrology as a cultural and symbolic interpretive tradition.','neutral','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrology','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002','misc','wiki_astrology','science_caution',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Scientific language caveat','When preparing astrology content, claims of scientific certainty should be avoided. Interpretations offered to the user should be written not as repeatable experimental results, but as guidance texts explained in the language of symbols, archetypes, and self-awareness.','A note on avoiding claims of scientific certainty in astrology interpretations.','professional','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrology','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000003','misc','wiki_astrology','barnum_effect',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Note on the Barnum effect','The perception of general and flattering statements as personally specific is a significant psychological risk in the astrology experience. LLM outputs should therefore reduce overly vague, one-size-fits-all sentences and build a more responsible language using specific details drawn from the user''s birth data, question context, and past interactions.','A Barnum-effect caveat for reducing generic, catch-all interpretations.','professional','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrology','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000004','misc','wiki_zodiac','geometry',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Zodiac geometry','In describing the zodiac, it can be recalled that the 360-degree celestial circle is symbolically divided into twelve equal parts. Each segment is treated as a 30-degree span; this approach describes the astrological symbolic order rather than constellation boundaries.','The division of the zodiac into twelve equal symbolic segments.','neutral','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zodiac','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000005','misc','wiki_zodiac','constellations',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Zodiac and constellations','The zodiac belt is related to the astronomical constellations; however, the sign symbols used in astrology are not directly the same as the modern constellation boundaries. When this distinction is made plainly in content, both the SEO text and user trust are strengthened.','The distinction between sign symbols and astronomical constellation boundaries.','neutral','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zodiac','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000006','misc','wiki_zodiac','ecliptic',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Ecliptic context','In sign and zodiac texts, the ecliptic context associated with the Sun''s apparent annual path across the sky can be used as a brief background. This information helps sign pages convey the idea of celestial coordinates and cycles rather than a mere "personality label."','A brief background linking the concept of the ecliptic to sign descriptions.','neutral','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrological_sign','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000007','misc','wiki_signs','elements',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Describing the elements','The fire, earth, air, and water elements can be used in sign content to explain basic temperament. Texts should avoid stereotyping; the element should be presented not as destiny on its own, but as a language of tendency read together with the other placements in the birth chart.','A note relating the elements to the whole chart without stereotyping.','warm','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrological_sign','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008','misc','wiki_signs','modalities',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Describing the modalities','The cardinal, fixed, and mutable modalities are a good editorial layer for explaining a sign''s mode of action. In profile texts, modality should be explained with plain examples through the rhythms of initiating, sustaining, and adapting.','A note explaining the modalities through the language of mode of action and rhythm.','warm','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrological_sign','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000009','misc','wiki_birth_chart','chart_context',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Birth chart context','When transitioning from sign pages to the birth chart, the user should be told clearly that the Sun sign alone does not explain the whole personality. A more layered picture emerges together with the Moon, ascendant, planets, houses, and aspects.','A CTA note transitioning from the Sun sign to the whole birth chart.','professional','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrological_sign','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000010','misc','wiki_astrology','traditions',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Astrological traditions','Astrology has various traditions, genres, and fields of practice across different cultures. In GoldMoodAstro content, this diversity should be conveyed in the language of "schools of interpretation" and "symbolic approaches" rather than a single absolute system narrative.','A note conveying different astrological traditions in a pluralistic way.','neutral','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrology','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000011','misc','wiki_astrology','responsible_copy',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — Responsible copy standard','Astrology texts should stay away from frightening, fatalistic, or definitive-outcome statements. The safest frame in the user experience is a guidance tone that emphasizes probability, awareness, the language of emotion, and the space for choice.','A product-language standard avoiding fatalistic and frightening statements.','professional','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrology','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),
('81100000-0000-4000-8000-000000000012','misc','wiki_zodiac','editorial_seo',NULL,'en','Wikipedia Import — SEO editorial bridge','When linking the sign, zodiac, and birth chart pages, the basic concept should be explained first, then move on to more personal and detailed interpretation. This structure both satisfies search intent and naturally carries the user toward the birth chart product.','An SEO content flow going from the basic concept to the personal chart.','professional','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zodiac','Wikipedia contributors, CC BY-SA 4.0',0,NULL,NULL),

